  [ David Kalnischkies ]
  * apt-pkg/deb/deblistparser.cc:
    - do not assume that the last char on a line is a \n (Closes: #633350)

 -- Michael Vogt <mvo@debian.org>  Thu, 28 Jul 2011 16:49:15 +0200

