  * apt.cron.daily: catch invalid dates due to DST time changes
    in the stamp files

  [ Michael Vogt ]
  * methods/gpgv.cc:
    - properly check for expired and revoked keys (closes: #433091)
  * apt-pkg/contrib/strutl.cc:
    - fix TimeToStr i18n (LP: #289807)
